  <original-body>* script/console is not usable under Windows with german keyboard. It's not even possible to write simple special characters like [].

* Rails console on Netbeans 6.1 is not starting.

Both problems are solved with this change: 

Changing the last line of \ruby\lib\ruby\gems\1.8\gems\rails-2.0.2\lib\commands\console.rb
from
exec &quot;#{options[:irb]} #{libs} --simple-prompt&quot;
to 
exec &quot;#{irb} #{libs} --noreadline --simple-prompt&quot;
helps.

This problem is known since rails-1.1.2 or even earlier versions.</original-body>
